<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">

    <PropertyGroup>
        <TargetFramework>netstandard2.0</TargetFramework>
        <ImplicitUsings>disable</ImplicitUsings>
        <Nullable>disable</Nullable>
        <GenerateDocumentationFile>true</GenerateDocumentationFile>
        <PackageReadmeFile>docs/README.md</PackageReadmeFile>
        <Description>Software development kit for the ProjectManager.com API for DotNet</Description>
        <PackageTags>projectmanager project management task tracking projects tasks</PackageTags>
        <Copyright>Copyright 2023 - 2025</Copyright>
        <PackageReleaseNotes>
# Patch notes for 144.0.155

These patch notes summarize the changes from version 143.0.162.

Added 2 new APIs:
* ProjectChargeCode.CreateProjectChargeCode (POST /api/data/projects/chargecodes)
* ProjectStatus.CreateProjectStatus (POST /api/data/projects/statuses)

Changes to data models:
* ProjectChargeCodeDto: Added new field `isActive`
* ProjectTemplateDto: Added new field `ownerId`
* ProjectTemplateDto: Added new field `createDate`
* TimesheetDto: Added new field `approvalStatusId`
* UserRoleDto: Added new field `description`
* UserRoleDto: Added new field `isAdmin`
* UserRoleDto: Added new field `isCustom`
* UserRoleDto: Added new field `isGlobalAdmin`
* UserRoleDto: Added new field `isGuest`
* UserRoleDto: Added new field `isDefault`
* UserRoleDto: Added new field `permissions`


        </PackageReleaseNotes>
        <PackageIcon>docs/logo.png</PackageIcon>
        <PackageLicenseExpression>MIT</PackageLicenseExpression>
		<version>144.0.155</version>
        <Authors>ProjectManager.com</Authors>
        <PublishRepositoryUrl>true</PublishRepositoryUrl>
    </PropertyGroup>

    <ItemGroup>
      <PackageReference Include="System.Text.Json" Version="9.0.0" />
    </ItemGroup>
    
    <ItemGroup>
        <None
                Include="../README.md"
                PackagePath="/docs"
                Pack="true" />
        <None
                Include="../LICENSE"
                PackagePath="/docs"
                Pack="true" />
        <None
                Include="../images/logo.png"
                PackagePath="/docs"
                Pack="true" />
    </ItemGroup>

</Project>
